Comment: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,Main,,0,0,0,,A
Dialogue: 0,0:00:05.19,0:00:09.20,Main,Ghiaccio,0,0,0,,I should be able to meet up with\N Melone in about an hour.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:09.20,0:00:13.12,Main,Risotto,0,0,0,,Ghiaccio, I'll leave the situation to you and Melone.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:13.58,0:00:15.41,Main,Risotto,0,0,0,,You can never be too careful.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:15.41,0:00:19.87,Main,Risotto,0,0,0,,I'll stay back and try to figure out\Nwhere they're headed based on their journey so far.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:19.87,0:00:21.92,Narrator,Ghiaccio,0,0,0,,Got it, Risotto.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:23.25,0:00:26.05,Main,Risotto,0,0,0,,How much longer are you going to make me wait? \NHurry up.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:26.05,0:00:28.59,Main,Risotto,0,0,0,,Restoring this should be trivial for you.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:30.47,0:00:31.76,Main,Guy,0,0,0,,Risotto...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:32.30,0:00:35.56,Main,Guy,0,0,0,,Do you really think you can \Nget away with betraying Passione?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:36.02,0:00:38.18,Main,Risotto,0,0,0,,We're running short on time.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:44.02,0:00:46.28,Main,Risotto,0,0,0,,Your left eye is next.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:46.28,0:00:48.82,Main,Risotto,0,0,0,,You only need a single hand and eye to work.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:48.82,0:00:51.41,Main,Guy,0,0,0,,Y-You should know better than anyone!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:51.41,0:00:55.08,Main,Guy,0,0,0,,All traitors, without exception, \Nwill be erased by the boss...{bosu kara"... I guess it could also mean that the boss will order them taken out, because it's not like he himself disposes of them. -Starfish}
