Dialogue: 0,0:02:28.92,0:02:30.96,Main,Babyface,0,0,0,,{\an8}Wh-What?! {Line 19-21 copied from episode 17 -Gyro}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:30.96,0:02:37.18,Main,Giorno,0,0,0,,{\an8}The hand I severed became \Na living creature and invaded your body!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:39.22,0:02:41.56,Main,Giorno,0,0,0,,As you can see, it became a piranha!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:50.53,0:02:54.57,Main,Giorno,0,0,0,,It has a large hole in its torso \Ngoing up to its neck...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:54.57,0:02:56.16,Main,Giorno,0,0,0,,...yet it can still move?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:57.66,0:03:00.28,Main,Melone,0,0,0,,Wh-What's wrong, Babyface?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:00.28,0:03:01.70,Main,Melone,0,0,0,,Answer me! Hey!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:03.71,0:03:06.67,Main,Babyface,0,0,0,,This is actual shit left behind by the tortoise!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:06.67,0:03:10.13,Main,Babyface,0,0,0,,Why am I the one \Nwho has to deal with this?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:10.13,0:03:12.05,Main,Babyface,0,0,0,,Dammit!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:12.05,0:03:14.38,Main,Babyface,0,0,0,,This pain in my heart...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:14.88,0:03:17.26,Main,Babyface,0,0,0,,You'll pay for this...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:17.89,0:03:21.47,Main,Babyface,0,0,0,,...by dying in disgrace!\N I'll make sure of it!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:21.89,0:03:27.44,Main,Giorno,0,0,0,,If Buccellati and Trish won't\N return to normal unless I defeat you...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:27.94,0:03:29.31,Main,Giorno,0,0,0,,...then that's what I'll do!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:29.77,0:03:30.98,Main,Giorno,0,0,0,,You can't escape!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:30.98,0:03:33.03,Main,Giorno,0,0,0,,I'm going for your head this time!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:33.03,0:03:34.94,Main,Babyface,0,0,0,,Just try me...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:35.53,0:03:37.24,Main,Babyface,0,0,0,,...you son of a bitch!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:40.16,0:03:41.41,Main,Melone,0,0,0,,This is bad...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:41.41,0:03:45.96,Main,Melone,0,0,0,,The downside to its automatic tracking \Nis that it doesn't always listen to me. {check this one Toni, it changes the meaning quite a bit}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:47.83,0:03:49.17,Main,Babyface,0,0,0,,Asshole!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:50.17,0:03:52.71,Main,Giorno,0,0,0,,You've already gouged out \Nthree pieces of my body...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:52.71,0:03:54.59,Main,Giorno,0,0,0,,I know the range of your attack!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:01.51,0:04:04.43,Main,Giorno,0,0,0,,Did its range...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:04.43,0:04:06.10,Main,Giorno,0,0,0,,...just extend itself?!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:11.52,0:04:13.19,Main,Melone,0,0,0,,He grew taller?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:13.19,0:04:15.82,Main,Melone,0,0,0,,His anger must have caused him to grow!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:15.82,0:04:17.28,Main,Melone,0,0,0,,Di molto!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:17.28,0:04:20.07,Main,Melone,0,0,0,,I knew that woman was\N the right person to be his mother!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:23.20,0:04:24.99,Main,Babyface,0,0,0,,Simple is best.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:24.99,0:04:29.21,Main,Babyface,0,0,0,,I'm gonna kill this asshole {\i1}my{\i0} way!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:29.75,0:04:31.50,Main,Giorno,0,0,0,,Bring it back, Gold Experience!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:31.92,0:04:33.54,Main,Babyface,0,0,0,,Die!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:36.63,0:04:37.47,Main,Giorno,0,0,0,,Muda!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:39.72,0:04:40.80,Main,Giorno,0,0,0,,A direct hit.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:44.31,0:04:45.97,Main,Babyface,0,0,0,,Take a good look.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:45.97,0:04:48.35,Main,Babyface,0,0,0,,You didn't hit my head!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:48.81,0:04:51.52,Main,Babyface,0,0,0,,I win! It's over!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:52.40,0:04:54.52,Main,Giorno,0,0,0,,I told you, it's pointless.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:58.90,0:05:00.91,Main,Babyface,0,0,0,,Wh-What the hell?!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:00.91,0:05:02.41,Main,Giorno,0,0,0,,Look again.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:02.41,0:05:06.74,Main,Giorno,0,0,0,,The object that returned to\N Gold Experience wasn't its own hand.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:08.12,0:05:09.79,Main,Giorno,0,0,0,,It was the motorcycle.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:09.79,0:05:13.00,Main,Giorno,0,0,0,,I imbued the motorcycle with life \Nand had it return as a hand.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:16.38,0:05:20.51,Main,Giorno,0,0,0,,You just assimilated the \Nmotorcycle into your body...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:21.09,0:05:22.30,Main,Giorno,0,0,0,,...as a part of you.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:22.30,0:05:24.47,Main,Babyface,0,0,0,,This is nothing...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:24.47,0:05:27.56,Main,Babyface,0,0,0,,I'll just split apart and get away aga{\fscx300}-{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:27.56,0:05:28.85,Main,Giorno,0,0,0,,Think about it...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:28.85,0:05:30.85,Main,Giorno,0,0,0,,Motorcycles contain gasoline.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:31.64,0:05:37.02,Main,Giorno,0,0,0,,I'm fairly certain I can create a large enough explosion\N to prevent you from escaping by splitting yourself apart.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:37.69,0:05:39.69,Main,Babyface,0,0,0,,What?!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:48.45,0:05:52.16,Main,Babyface,0,0,0,,Sizzling... Burning...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:52.71,0:05:57.88,Main,Giorno,0,0,0,,It seems as though doing things \Nyour way was pointless... in the end.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:01.13,0:06:03.01,Main,Melone,0,0,0,,I-It disappeared?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:03.01,0:06:04.55,Main,Melone,0,0,0,,My contact with it disappeared?!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:04.55,0:06:06.64,Main,Melone,0,0,0,,Damn! This is absurd!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:06.64,0:06:08.14,Main,Melone,0,0,0,,That new guy!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:13.90,0:06:14.90,Main,Bruno,0,0,0,,He did it...{It really speaks to how accustomed these guys are to dealing with crazy shit that THIS is his entire reaction... -Starfish}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:26.87,0:06:28.70,Main,Ghiaccio,0,0,0,,It should be somewhere around here...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:29.33,0:06:33.33,Main,Guy,0,0,0,,My car's gone!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:30.12,0:06:33.33,Secondary,Lady,0,0,0,,Where's my car? Who stole it?!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:33.33,0:06:36.29,Main,Ghiaccio,0,0,0,,That's Melone's motorcycle...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:36.29,0:06:42.76,Main,Ghiaccio,0,0,0,,I was told to ask around, \Ndig up whatever dirt will help me find them...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:42.76,0:06:45.13,Main,Ghiaccio,0,0,0,,The digging part I get.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:45.13,0:06:47.22,Main,Ghiaccio,0,0,0,,It makes perfect sense.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:47.22,0:06:50.47,Main,Ghiaccio,0,0,0,,It's like digging for stuff hidden in the ground.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:51.18,0:06:54.89,Main,Ghiaccio,0,0,0,,But why the flying fuck \Nwould you dig up dirt?!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:54.89,0:06:56.40,Main,Ghiaccio,0,0,0,,Dirt is fucking everywhere!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:56.40,0:06:57.86,Main,Ghiaccio,0,0,0,,Jesus fuck!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:57.86,0:06:59.15,Main,Ghiaccio,0,0,0,,What fucking bullshit is that?!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:59.15,0:07:01.61,Main,Ghiaccio,0,0,0,,Who the fuck digs up dirt looking for dirt?!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:01.61,0:07:04.03,Main,Ghiaccio,0,0,0,,Do I look fucking retarded?!\N Goddammit!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:05.78,0:07:09.74,Narrator,Ghiaccio,0,0,0,,Hey, Melone! \NI can't find shit on Buccellati and his crew!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:11.20,0:07:13.62,Narrator,Ghiaccio,0,0,0,,You getting this? Hello?!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:13.62,0:07:15.33,Main,Melone,0,0,0,,I can hear you.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:15.33,0:07:17.92,Main,Melone,0,0,0,,But I'm not giving up just yet!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:18.42,0:07:20.88,Main,Melone,0,0,0,,I still have Buccellati's blood!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:20.88,0:07:23.26,Main,Melone,0,0,0,,I can produce as many Juniors as we need!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:24.09,0:07:26.22,Main,Melone,0,0,0,,I'll send one in pursuit right away!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:27.51,0:07:29.68,Main,Ghiaccio,0,0,0,,You'd better, Melone.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:29.68,0:07:32.18,Main,Melone,0,0,0,,We need to take the new guy more seriously.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:32.18,0:07:34.14,Main,Melone,0,0,0,,He should be the first one we eliminate.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:35.98,0:07:38.60,Main,Melone,0,0,0,,I'll find an even better mother...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:39.48,0:07:43.07,Main,Melone,0,0,0,,...and create a powered-up, completely invincible...{I really don't like this split but given the long pause he takes and how "Junior" is the first word he says after said pause... it's kinda inevitable I guess -.- -Starfish}{I completely agree. I hate this split. I tried to combine it but that pause is just a bit too long D: -Gyro}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:44.61,0:07:47.53,Main,Melone,0,0,0,,...Junior who will track them down.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:50.07,0:07:51.99,Main,Melone,0,0,0,,What was that?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:52.74,0:07:54.20,Main,Melone,0,0,0,,It looked like a snake...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:54.50,0:07:56.29,Narrator,Ghiaccio,0,0,0,,What? What's wrong?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:56.29,0:07:58.67,Main,Melone,0,0,0,,What is a snake doing at a station in Rome?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:03.59,0:08:05.05,Main,Melone,0,0,0,,I-It's burning!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:05.46,0:08:08.59,Main,Melone,0,0,0,,This is... the new guy's ability...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:08.59,0:08:11.26,Main,Melone,0,0,0,,He must have used the Junior's corpse to{\fscx300}-{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:17.98,0:08:19.60,Narrator,Ghiaccio,0,0,0,,Hello?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:19.60,0:08:22.69,Narrator,Ghiaccio,0,0,0,,Hey, Melone!\N What the fuck?! Hey!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:25.32,0:08:30.32,Main,Giorno,0,0,0,,The venomous snake I sent to Roma Termini Station \Njust turned back into part of the enemy.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:30.32,0:08:33.58,Main,Fugo,0,0,0,,The user is eliminated. \NThat makes five.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:33.58,0:08:38.16,Main,Fugo,0,0,0,,If our intel is correct, \Nonly two members of the Hitman Team remain.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:38.16,0:08:40.37,Main,Mista,0,0,0,,We still gotta be careful.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:40.75,0:08:42.84,Main,Mista,0,0,0,,Now let's get to Venice already!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:44.84,0:08:47.05,Main,Ghiaccio,0,0,0,,Now Melone, too?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:48.22,0:08:50.55,Main,Ghiaccio,0,0,0,,Fuck! Fuck! Fuck!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:50.55,0:08:52.18,Main,Ghiaccio,0,0,0,,Motherfucker!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:53.97,0:08:55.60,Narrator,Ghiaccio,0,0,0,,Hello?!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:55.60,0:08:58.68,Main,Risotto,0,0,0,,It's me.\N I managed to finish the analysis.
Comment: 0,0:08:58.68,0:08:59.35,Narrator,Ghiaccio,0,0,0,,Huh?!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:59.85,0:09:01.81,Main,Risotto,0,0,0,,I'm sending you the data as we speak.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:10.74,0:09:12.78,Main,Bruno,0,0,0,,We just received a new order from the boss.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:13.74,0:09:17.16,Main,Bruno,0,0,0,,Abbacchio, could you come over here next to the chair?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:17.16,0:09:17.87,Main,Abbacchio,0,0,0,,Me? {No, the other Abbacchio}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:19.83,0:09:21.33,Main,Bruno,0,0,0,,Here's the order.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:21.33,0:09:27.42,Main,Abbacchio,0,0,0,,"Have Abbacchio use his Moody Blues \Nnear the dining chair and rewind to just over 14 hours ago."
Dialogue: 0,0:09:27.42,0:09:31.93,Main,Bruno,0,0,0,,Someone else was inside the tortoise before us.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:31.93,0:09:33.22,Main,Bruno,0,0,0,,I believe that's what he's getting at.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:33.55,0:09:34.97,Main,Abbacchio,0,0,0,,Got it.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:34.97,0:09:37.47,Main,Abbacchio,0,0,0,,I'll start looking from about fifteen hours ago.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:44.52,0:09:45.73,Main,Abbacchio,0,0,0,,It transformed.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:47.48,0:09:49.99,Main,Narancia,0,0,0,,Hey, that old dude looks familiar!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:49.99,0:09:51.74,Main,Bruno,0,0,0,,That's the capo, Mr. Pericolo!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:51.74,0:09:56.53,Main,Bruno,0,0,0,,So he was the one who placed the tortoise near the water fountain at Naples Station.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:56.53,0:10:00.45,Main,Abbacchio,0,0,0,,And approximately fourteen hours ago,\N he entered this tortoise.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:01.21,0:10:02.41,Main,Abbacchio,0,0,0,,I'm continuing the replay.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:03.79,0:10:08.88,Main,Pericolo,0,0,0,,Buccellati and team, \NI will now give you your final order.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:09.59,0:10:10.63,Main,Bruno,0,0,0,,Final order?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:11.09,0:10:16.39,Main,Pericolo,0,0,0,,I'm using this method to give you the message\N in order to prevent it from falling into the wrong hands.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:16.39,0:10:20.31,Main,Pericolo,0,0,0,,What I'm about to tell you is of utmost importance and must remain between us.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:20.31,0:10:23.85,Main,Pericolo,0,0,0,,I'm going to tell you how to \Nhand Trish off to the boss.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:24.48,0:10:25.56,Main,Bruno,0,0,0,,How we're going...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:25.56,0:10:26.94,Main,Narancia,0,0,0,,...to hand her over? {Lol this is such a One Piece moment. I can totally imagine one of the straw hats starting the sentence and the other finishing it thanks to their psychic connection. Now all we need is a large mob of random people yelling very long lines of dialogue in perfect timing -Gyro}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:27.57,0:10:29.36,Main,Pericolo,0,0,0,,Listen closely, now.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:29.36,0:10:31.57,Main,Pericolo,0,0,0,,Once you've safely arrived in Venice...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:31.57,0:10:37.24,Main,Pericolo,0,0,0,,...go to this sculpture and retrieve \Nthe OA-DISC that's inside.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:37.24,0:10:41.41,Main,Pericolo,0,0,0,,It contains data that will instruct you on how to hand her over.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:42.54,0:10:44.21,Main,Narancia,0,0,0,,Hey! He burned it!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:44.21,0:10:45.88,Main,Bruno,0,0,0,,Abbacchio, pause it!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:45.88,0:10:46.79,Main,Abbacchio,0,0,0,,Right.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:48.79,0:10:51.55,Main,Bruno,0,0,0,,I'm pretty sure this is \Nthe entrance to Venice...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:51.88,0:10:53.63,Main,Bruno,0,0,0,,Right in front of Santa Lucia Station.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:54.01,0:10:55.51,Main,Bruno,0,0,0,,The lion statue is there.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:56.72,0:10:58.10,Main,Pericolo,0,0,0,,That is all.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:58.10,0:11:00.93,Main,Pericolo,0,0,0,,Obtain the OA-DISC at all costs.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:00.93,0:11:03.56,Main,Pericolo,0,0,0,,My identity has been compromised.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:03.56,0:11:10.32,Main,Pericolo,0,0,0,,Nothing is more important right now \Nthan bringing Trish to her father, the boss.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:10.32,0:11:12.69,Main,Pericolo,0,0,0,,No evidence can be left behind.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:13.49,0:11:20.91,Main,Pericolo,0,0,0,,Thanks to the boss, I've been able to live a wealthy, blessed, and fulfilling life.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:21.33,0:11:23.41,Main,Pericolo,0,0,0,,My mission is over.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:25.50,0:11:28.88,Main,Pericolo,0,0,0,,From the bottom of my heart, \NI pray for your success.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:33.55,0:11:36.63,Main,Narancia,0,0,0,,What the hell?!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:44.48,0:11:45.81,Main,Bruno,0,0,0,,Mr. Pericolo...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:55.40,0:11:58.66,Main,Diavolo,0,0,0,,They should have received the order by now. {IT MAKES ME SO HAPPY TO SEE DIAVOLO AS THE LISTED ACTOR AAAAAAAAAAH -Gyro}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:02.66,0:12:08.12,Main,Diavolo,0,0,0,,Obtaining the disc, let alone reaching me, \Nwill prove difficult for them.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:09.12,0:12:11.63,Main,Diavolo,0,0,0,,The most important thing is \Nwhat awaits at the end...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:12.34,0:12:15.67,Main,Diavolo,0,0,0,,Bring my daughter Trish here...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:18.01,0:12:19.89,Main,Diavolo,0,0,0,,...to Venice.
Comment: 0,0:12:24.01,0:12:24.06,Main,,0,0,0,,C
Dialogue: 0,0:12:28.85,0:12:33.15,Narrator,Narrator,0,0,0,,The fortress city of the sea, \Nfloating amidst the morning haze: Venice.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:33.15,0:12:37.70,Narrator,Narrator,0,0,0,,There is only one way to get there \Nby car from the mainland.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:37.70,0:12:42.53,Narrator,Narrator,0,0,0,,It is a bridge which stretches for 3.5 kilometers \Nover the sea known as the Ponte della Libertà. {https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Ponte_della_Libert%C3%A0}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:42.95,0:12:45.41,Narrator,Narrator,0,0,0,,The station lies just beyond it.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:45.41,0:12:49.87,Narrator,Narrator,0,0,0,,The lion statue where the target disc is hidden \Ncan be found in a square there.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:54.46,0:12:57.92,Main,Mista,0,0,0,,Giorno, so far I haven't seen anyone tailing us.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:57.92,0:13:00.59,Main,Giorno,0,0,0,,Yes. No one in front of us, either.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:00.59,0:13:02.47,Main,Giorno,0,0,0,,The city is still asleep.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:02.47,0:13:04.60,Main,Giorno,0,0,0,,We're the only car on the road.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:05.10,0:13:07.68,Main,Mista,0,0,0,,Why do the windows keep fogging up so quickly?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:12.77,0:13:14.15,Main,Mista,0,0,0,,What the hell?!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:14.15,0:13:15.44,Main,Giorno,0,0,0,,My apologies.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:15.44,0:13:17.48,Main,Giorno,0,0,0,,The tires just slipped a bit.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:17.48,0:13:19.70,Main,Mista,0,0,0,,On a straight bridge like this?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:19.70,0:13:22.61,Main,Mista,0,0,0,,Try to be more careful! \NDo you even have a license?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:22.61,0:13:24.62,Main,Giorno,0,0,0,,No. I'm only fifteen.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:28.33,0:13:32.00,Main,Mista,0,0,0,,What's that thing stuck on the window?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:32.00,0:13:34.04,Main,Mista,0,0,0,,It's on the inside.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:34.04,0:13:37.55,Main,Mista,0,0,0,,I didn't notice it when \NI was looking outside earlier...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:37.55,0:13:39.34,Main,Mista,0,0,0,,No, wait a second...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:39.67,0:13:41.72,Main,Mista,0,0,0,,That shape...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:41.72,0:13:43.05,Main,Mista,0,0,0,,It's... a finger!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:48.47,0:13:50.39,Main,Giorno,0,0,0,,Let's open the windows a bit.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:50.39,0:13:53.69,Main,Giorno,0,0,0,,The windows are fogging up from the \Ntemperature difference inside and out of the car.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:54.61,0:13:57.23,Main,Giorno,0,0,0,,Wh-What?! \NWhat's with this wind pressure?!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:58.82,0:14:02.53,Main,Ghiaccio,0,0,0,,At first, we were frozen with fear... But...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:02.95,0:14:10.20,Main,Ghiaccio,0,0,0,,With the help of a computer, it wasn't too hard to recreate the ashes that were lying next to Pericolo in the photo.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:10.66,0:14:12.08,Main,Ghiaccio,0,0,0,,You guys fucking clueless!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:12.83,0:14:16.09,Main,Ghiaccio,0,0,0,,You'll never get away from the Hitman Team!{I'm just WAITING for him to call them "Damn nerds" and create explosions from his hands at this point. -Starfish}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:16.09,0:14:19.34,Main,Giorno,0,0,0,,It's an enemy! \NThey got on the roof of the car without us realizing it!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:19.34,0:14:22.84,Main,Giorno,0,0,0,,Mista, what are you doing? \NShoot the enemy through the roof!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:22.84,0:14:26.68,Main,Mista,0,0,0,,The car is being chilled crazy fast right now...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:26.68,0:14:34.06,Main,Mista,0,0,0,,It's so fast that my finger froze to the window and snapped off before I even felt the cold.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:34.98,0:14:38.94,Main,Mista,0,0,0,,If I don't peel my face off the window, \Nmy brain will freeze up.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:38.94,0:14:41.78,Main,Mista,0,0,0,,Not sure I'm ready to sacrifice my face, though.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:42.40,0:14:44.78,Main,Ghiaccio,0,0,0,,Where's the tortoise?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:44.78,0:14:47.37,Main,Ghiaccio,0,0,0,,I don't see the tortoise in the car.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:47.62,0:14:51.25,Main,Ghiaccio,0,0,0,,You two aren't with Trish and Buccellati?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:51.25,0:14:54.50,Main,Ghiaccio,0,0,0,,If you went through the trouble of splitting up...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:54.50,0:14:55.96,Main,Ghiaccio,0,0,0,,I got it!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:55.96,0:14:59.96,Main,Ghiaccio,0,0,0,,You must be on a mission\N to get something {\i1}really{\i0} important!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:59.96,0:15:01.63,Main,Ghiaccio,0,0,0,,The location in the picture...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:01.63,0:15:03.76,Main,Ghiaccio,0,0,0,,It has to be at the station in Venice!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:05.13,0:15:07.55,Thoughts,Mista,0,0,0,,Blood finally spurted from my hand!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:10.51,0:15:11.97,Main,Sex Pistols,0,0,0,,Yeehaw!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:15.06,0:15:17.06,Main,Sex Pistols,0,0,0,,I-Ice!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:17.48,0:15:20.73,Main,Sex Pistols,0,0,0,,He covered himself in ice and \Nfroze himself to the roof of the car!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:20.73,0:15:23.90,Main,Sex Pistols,0,0,0,,The bullets can't get through to him!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:24.57,0:15:25.49,Main,Sex Pistols,0,0,0,,What the...?!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:25.49,0:15:28.70,Main,Sex Pistols,0,0,0,,N-No! \NWe're starting to freeze, too!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:29.78,0:15:31.41,Main,Sex Pistols,0,0,0,,Save me!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:31.41,0:15:32.91,Main,Sex Pistols,0,0,0,,Number Two!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:32.91,0:15:33.75,Main,Sex Pistols,0,0,0,,Don't go!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:35.21,0:15:37.92,Main,Sex Pistols,0,0,0,,Number Two! \NNumber Three!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:38.79,0:15:40.75,Main,Mista,0,0,0,,What?!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:42.71,0:15:47.43,Main,Mista,0,0,0,,A-All I did was blink, \Nand now my eyelashes are stuck together!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:48.97,0:15:51.51,Main,Giorno,0,0,0,,He must have positioned himself \Non the roof on purpose!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:51.85,0:15:55.60,Main,Giorno,0,0,0,,The car is currently going \Neighty kilometers per hour.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:55.60,0:15:56.98,Main,Giorno,0,0,0,,Which means...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:56.98,0:16:00.19,Main,Giorno,0,0,0,,It's similar to being stuck in \Ntwenty meter per second wind.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:00.61,0:16:05.11,Main,Giorno,0,0,0,,The effective temperature drops by 1° Celsius \Nfor every meter of wind velocity...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:05.36,0:16:09.03,Main,Giorno,0,0,0,,...so the air around us has chilled to -20° Celsius!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:09.03,0:16:10.45,Main,Mista,0,0,0,,Then stop the damn car!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:10.45,0:16:13.24,Main,Mista,0,0,0,,Why the hell are you still flooring it?!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:13.49,0:16:15.79,Main,Giorno,0,0,0,,Yes. I'm trying to...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:15.79,0:16:19.54,Main,Giorno,0,0,0,,But the brake pedal is frozen and won't go down!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:19.54,0:16:21.04,Main,Giorno,0,0,0,,I'm losing the steering wheel, too!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:21.04,0:16:23.96,Main,Giorno,0,0,0,,The engine is still running and seemingly won't stop!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:27.47,0:16:31.51,Main,Giorno,0,0,0,,The surface of the car has to have \Nreached -100° Celsius by now!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:31.80,0:16:35.52,Main,Giorno,0,0,0,,And at incredible speed! \NSo this is... the enemy's ability!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:37.48,0:16:42.15,Main,Mista,0,0,0,,Th-The blood that was spurting out of my hand froze...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:43.36,0:16:47.19,Main,Mista,0,0,0,,And the moisture from my breathing\N caused my nostrils to freeze together...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:48.65,0:16:50.28,Main,Mista,0,0,0,,And now my lips...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:50.28,0:16:51.87,Main,Mista,0,0,0,,Shit! I can't breathe!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:52.32,0:16:53.91,Main,Mista,0,0,0,,S-Stop the car, Giorno!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:53.91,0:16:56.25,Main,Mista,0,0,0,,Can't you can turn the car \Ninto a frog or something?!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:56.25,0:16:58.37,Main,Mista,0,0,0,,Use your ability somehow!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:58.37,0:17:00.87,Main,Giorno,0,0,0,,I've already tried that...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:00.87,0:17:05.17,Main,Giorno,0,0,0,,But there are no organisms \Nthat can be born at -100° Celsius!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:09.22,0:17:11.26,Main,Ghiaccio,0,0,0,,You know about Paris, France?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:11.26,0:17:13.80,Main,Ghiaccio,0,0,0,,In English, they pronounce it "Paris"...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:13.80,0:17:17.35,Main,Ghiaccio,0,0,0,,But everyone else pronounces it \Nwithout the "s" sound, like the French do.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:17.35,0:17:21.40,Main,Ghiaccio,0,0,0,,But with Venezia, everyone pronounces \Nit the English way, "Venice".
Dialogue: 0,0:17:21.77,0:17:25.57,Main,Ghiaccio,0,0,0,,As in, {\i1}The Merchant of Venice{\i0} \Nand {\i1}Death in Venice{\i0}...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:26.15,0:17:31.11,Main,Ghiaccio,0,0,0,,Why isn't the title {\i1}Death in Venezia?!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:17:31.11,0:17:32.70,Main,Ghiaccio,0,0,0,,Are they fucking mocking me?!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:32.70,0:17:35.58,Main,Ghiaccio,0,0,0,,Use the Italian word \Nsince it takes place here, fuckheads!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:35.58,0:17:38.25,Main,Ghiaccio,0,0,0,,This shit pisses me off!\N Are they seriously fucking mocking me?!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:38.25,0:17:39.83,Main,Ghiaccio,0,0,0,,Fucking morons!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:44.79,0:17:47.71,Main,Ghiaccio,0,0,0,,Looks like they're starting \Nto have trouble driving...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:47.71,0:17:49.30,Main,Giorno,0,0,0,,Mista...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:49.30,0:17:53.09,Main,Giorno,0,0,0,,My Gold Experience needs heat.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:53.09,0:17:56.93,Main,Giorno,0,0,0,,So unfortunately, the most I can do for you...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:57.22,0:17:59.89,Main,Giorno,0,0,0,,...is pick up these bullets...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:00.52,0:18:04.31,Main,Ghiaccio,0,0,0,,You won't be able to fill the car\N with any more holes!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:04.31,0:18:06.94,Main,Ghiaccio,0,0,0,,I'll just freeze you to an even lower temp{\fscx300}-{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:18:13.78,0:18:17.12,Main,Mista,0,0,0,,Bullets create heat from being fired, don't they?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:17.12,0:18:20.62,Main,Mista,0,0,0,,So by firing the bullets Giorno picked up for me...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:20.62,0:18:21.91,Main,Mista,0,0,0,,...I'm making heat!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:21.91,0:18:26.67,Main,Mista,0,0,0,,I guess I'll go ahead and \Ndo the honors for Giorno while I'm at it...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:27.25,0:18:29.50,Main,Mista,0,0,0,,Gold Experience!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:36.85,0:18:38.14,Main,Mista,0,0,0,,We did it!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:38.14,0:18:45.19,Main,Mista,0,0,0,,Plant roots have the energy to prop up \Nasphalt in roads and even shatter rocks!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:45.19,0:18:48.40,Main,Mista,0,0,0,,Keep hold of the steering wheel, Giorno! \NWe're gonna make a break for it!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:58.45,0:19:01.95,Main,Ghiaccio,0,0,0,,So that must be the new guy's ability Melone mentioned.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:01.95,0:19:04.29,Main,Ghiaccio,0,0,0,,But you're not getting away!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:08.21,0:19:09.75,Main,Mista,0,0,0,,Seriously? What an asshole!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:09.75,0:19:11.71,Main,Mista,0,0,0,,He's still coming after us!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:11.71,0:19:16.22,Main,Ghiaccio,0,0,0,,I, Ghiaccio,{He's Dio now. Deal with it. (Well actually I just wanted to keep this in to make it so his name isn't said only ONCE, before we even see him.) -Starfish} will be taking \Nwhatever's at the station, no matter what.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:18.72,0:19:20.60,Main,Ghiaccio,0,0,0,,You're wasting your bullets.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:20.60,0:19:28.19,Main,Ghiaccio,0,0,0,,My ability, White Album, freezes the moisture in the air\N to an extremely low temperature, letting me wear it like armor!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:29.40,0:19:36.49,Main,Ghiaccio,0,0,0,,Not only does it allow me to skate, \Nit also gives me enough power to shrug off your pathetic bullets!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:37.11,0:19:38.57,Main,Mista,0,0,0,,Step on it, Giorno!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:38.57,0:19:40.16,Main,Giorno,0,0,0,,I can't go any faster!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:40.16,0:19:41.95,Main,Giorno,0,0,0,,The tires are still slipping!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:41.95,0:19:45.00,Main,Giorno,0,0,0,,But worst of all, they know our plan!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:45.00,0:19:48.42,Main,Mista,0,0,0,,They don't know where the tortoise and Trish are...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:48.42,0:19:51.92,Main,Mista,0,0,0,,...so if you look on the bright side, \Nwe're not totally fucked.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:51.92,0:19:54.97,Main,Giorno,0,0,0,,Optimistic as usual, aren't you?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:54.97,0:19:56.17,Main,Giorno,0,0,0,,You're a strange man.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:56.47,0:19:58.43,Main,Mista,0,0,0,,He's coming! \NFloor it! Faster!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:58.43,0:19:59.72,Main,Giorno,0,0,0,,I told you, I can't!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:59.72,0:20:02.26,Main,Giorno,0,0,0,,If we slip, we'll lose even more sp{\fscx300}-{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:02.26,0:20:04.85,Main,Mista,0,0,0,,Just do it, dammit! \NFloor it!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:04.85,0:20:07.23,Main,Ghiaccio,0,0,0,,I told you, you're wasting your time!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:07.23,0:20:09.77,Main,Mista,0,0,0,,Number Three and Number Two \Nup on the roof, come back!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:16.28,0:20:18.57,Main,Mista,0,0,0,,Here's hoping you share a long kiss...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:18.57,0:20:23.33,Main,Mista,0,0,0,,...with Madame Concrete. \NAll the speed you've built up should make it extra passionate!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:27.71,0:20:29.04,Main,Sex Pistols,0,0,0,,Yeah!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:29.42,0:20:31.13,Main,Mista,0,0,0,,Good. We lost him!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:31.13,0:20:34.05,Main,Mista,0,0,0,,Now get us into the city \Nand head straight for the station!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:36.92,0:20:41.51,Main,Mista,0,0,0,,Before he can catch up to us, \Nwe'll get our hands on the disc and hide!
